description: Fix update error for 0.2.x users & add missing manifests
changelog:
**Bug Fixes:**
- fix(update): add defensive check for undefined item.from in orphanedMigrations
- Add missing manifests: 0.2.12, 0.2.13, 0.3.0-beta.1~6, 0.3.0-beta.11

Fixes "path argument must be of type string" error when upgrading from 0.2.12/0.2.13.
notes: Recommended for users who encountered update errors from 0.2.x versions.
